Package pddl4j.exp.fcomp

This package contains the classes relative to compared functions expressions of the PDDL language.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
EqualComp This class implements the equality comparaison function add of the pddl language.
FCompExp This class implements a compared function.
GEqualComp This class implements the greater or equal compared function add of the pddl language.
GreaterComp This class implements the greater compared function add of the pddl language.
LEqualComp This class implements the less or equal compared function add of the pddl language.
LessComp This class implements the less compared function add of the pddl language.
 

Enum Summary
